Overall response time

Overall there is a wide variation in response time for all calls over the whole data set. The average is 45.4116659 minutes, the median 8.0666667 minutes, the maximum 132.5843866 days, and then there are some negative numbers in there (the shortest response time being -717.4166667 minutes). This is just under 720, minutes which is 12 hours - so we can assume what is happening is the selection of the wrong time out by 12 hours. To fix this, add 720 to all negative time results.
